parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause fires, loss of power, and unexpected shutdowns, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
The failure of the sliding door actuator can cause the door to become stuck, unable to open or close, posing a safety risk in emergency situations.
symptoms: The door tries to open on its own
the door will not open or close
and the door will not latch.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and become difficult to control, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
and the vehicle will not shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to shut off unexpectedly, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts off while driving

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Air Conditioning and Blower Motor Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning and blower motor can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The vents do not blow full force
the air conditioning system does not work properly

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Oil Leaks and Oil Filter Housing Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine oil leaks and oil filter housing failure can cause engine damage, overheating, and potentially lead to a fire, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cylinder head failure and misfires can cause engine stalling, loss of power, and rough engine performance, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission oil cooler lines leaking and TIPM failure can cause transmission failure, loss of motive power, and accidents.

symptoms: hitting the driver or passenger in the back of the head
causing whiplash or other injuries. The headrest may not reset and remains in a deployed position
